thread.title: Soap EastEnders

author: Fiona Flynn
title: Soap EastEnders
text: Shocked by what she has seen, Donna confronts Les and Claudette, who both insist that they're not having an affair, but Donna's having none of it. Question is, will she tell Pam? Also today, Kathy and Ben come up with a plan to get more money, but think they may have some trouble trying to get Jane on board. Elsewhere, Kim thinks Ronnie may be stalking Vincent... eeek, if only she knew the half of it. While Shabnam finally opens up to Stacey about the death of her son.
